<%= provide(:body_id, 'index') %>
<%= provide(:result, '报表查看') %>

<div class="container-fluid content-wrapper">
  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <div class="hero-unit">
        <button type="button" class="close hidden-phone" data-dismiss="alert">&times;</button>
        <h1>选择对应的自租出口查询</h1>

        <p>
          本排名表根据各个出口对同一网站的各项测试得分进行统计，只统计总分此项指标，如对结果有异议，可申请核对。<br>
          下列出口与网站对应负分排名是根据最近一周的得分计算得出的数据，取其负分最高的前五项列表如下示。
        </p>
        <br/>

        <p class="hidden-phone">
          <a class="btn btn-info btn-large pull-right">详细指南请猛击此处 &raquo;...</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%= label_tag(:dest_node_name, '请选择具体的网站') %>
  <%= form_tag('website_ranking', :method => 'post', class: 'form-inline') do %>
    <%= select_tag :dest_node_name, options_from_collection_for_select(@tdn, 'dest_url', 'dest_node_name') -%>
    <%= submit_tag('查 询', class: 'btn btn-info span2') %>
  <% end %>
  <p></p>

  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <div class="row-fluid hidden-desktop hidden-phone">
        <% @out_data.each_with_index do |wline, i| %>
          <% unless wline[0].blank? %>
            <div class="span3">
              <h5 class="title"><%= wline[0] %>负分排名表：</h5>

              <div class="squiggly-border"></div>
              <table class="table table-striped table-bordered table-radmin">
                <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th style="text-align:center;">网站名称</th>
                  <th style="text-align:center;">负值</th>
                </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                <% wline[1].each do |odata| %>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="text-align:center;"><%= odata[0] %></td>
                    <td style="text-align:center;"><%= odata[1] %></td>
                  </tr>
                <% end %>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <h4 class="title">名言警句</h4>

      <div class="squiggly-border"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <blockquote>
        <p>
          Etiam varius erat in nisl egestas id auctor lacus consectetur.
          Ut dui risus, auctor a malesuada volutpat, tempus sit amet arcu.
        </p>
        <small class="pull-right">Jane Doe via Mobile</small>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>